history.content:
Looking for summer internships? Want to network with industry professionals? Check out our annual corporate event - Evening with Industry on Tuesday, November 3rd!

EWI is an annual career fair and networking dinner hosted by UC Berkeley’s Society of Women Engineers for ALL engineering students at Cal. Last year, we hosted 150 of UC Berkeley’s brightest and most dedicated engineering students to meet with company representatives across various engineering fields.

If you are looking for an internship or a full-time position, Evening with Industry is a great opportunity to meet recruiters and professionals! ALL genders are welcome! To register for the event, click here.

For more information, look here: https://www.facebook.com/events/639387142867543/
